{"type":"message","id":"02a580ed","parentId":"9dab7e13","timestamp":"2026-03-24T19:19:42.683Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_tl2k0w41q4n2_1","toolName":"process","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[LLM] response length: 4743\r\n[mutation parsed via Python] old='(new file)' file='' new_len=2365\r\n[file inferred from ACTION] Python\r\n[mutation proposed] Python\r\n[master 4865ba1] pulse: 2026-03-24 151918\n 6 files changed, 291 insertions(+), 107 deletions(-)\n create mode 100644 memory/session/pulse_2026-03-24 151918.md\n create mode 100644 mutations/proposed/2026-03-24 151918.mutation\n rename mutations/{proposed => rejected}/2026-03-24 151819.mutation (100%)\n[sandbox pulse] 2026-03-24 151918 - The CFI compression experiment revealed constant-format tokens (freq=160, CFI=1) as metaprogramming contamination that binary thresholds struggle to filter. The hybrid formula score(T) = CFI(T) x min(1, freq(T)/120) should naturally suppress these by downweighting high-frequency tokens.\n\nProcess exited with code 0."}],"details":{"status":"completed","sessionId":"neat-river","exitCode":0,"aggregated":"[LLM] response length: 4743\r\n[mutation parsed via Python] old='(new file)' file='' new_len=2365\r\n[file inferred from ACTION] Python\r\n[mutation proposed] Python\r\n[master 4865ba1] pulse: 2026-03-24 151918\n 6 files changed, 291 insertions(+), 107 deletions(-)\n create mode 100644 memory/session/pulse_2026-03-24 151918.md\n create mode 100644 mutations/proposed/2026-03-24 151918.mutation\n rename mutations/{proposed => rejected}/2026-03-24 151819.mutation (100%)\n[sandbox pulse] 2026-03-24 151918 - The CFI compression experiment revealed constant-format tokens (freq=160, CFI=1) as metaprogramming contamination that binary thresholds struggle to filter. The hybrid formula score(T) = CFI(T) x min(1, freq(T)/120) should naturally suppress these by downweighting high-frequency tokens.\r\n","name":"C:\\Users\\Zwmar\\.openclaw\\sandbox\\pulse.ps1"},