{"type":"message","id":"8b754b7f","parentId":"187bbc95","timestamp":"2026-03-24T19:19:55.146Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_56isoch121yo_2","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# CFI Hybrid Scoring Experiment - Strategy C Validation\nGenerated: 2026-03-24\n\n## Objective\nTest hypothesis: `score(T) = CFI(T) × min(1, freq(T)/120)` distinguishes:\n- Constant format (freq≈160, CFI≈1, score≈1.0) → metaprogramming artifact\n- Research trajectory (freq<120, CFI>0.5, score>0.4) → true causal content\n\n## Experiment Design\n- Dataset: 200 pulses from corpus\n- Train/Test split: 80/20\n- Metric: Precision and recall for research trajectory identification\n\n## Token Categories (from CFI_COMPRESSION_SYNTHESIS.md)\n| Token | Freq | CFI | Score | Classification |\n|-------|------|-----|-------|----------------|\n| \"for next instantiation\" | 160 | 1.00 | 1.00 | constant-format (expected to filter) |\n| \"pulse\" | 160 | 1.00 | 1.00 | constant-format (expected to filter) |\n| \"completed at:\" | 160 | 1.00 | 1.00 | constant-format (expected to filter) |\n| \"Phase 1\" | 136 | 0.96 | 0.96 | research trajectory (KEEP) |\n| \"Phase 0\" | 85 | 0.89 | 0.74 | research trajectory (KEEP) |\n| \"CFI\" | 112 | 0.72 | 0.60 | research trajectory (KEEP) |\n| \"architecture\" | 45 | 0.68 | 0.23 | research trajectory (KEEP) |\n\n## Scoring Formula\n```powershell\n$score = $cfi * [Math]::Min(1, $freq / 120)\n```\n\n## Hypothesis Test\nIf score > 0.4 → classify as research trajectory\nExpected result:\n- Constant format (freq=160, CFI=1): score=1.0 (BUT these need separate filter)\n- Research trajectory (freq<120, CFI>0.5): score > 0.4 (KEEP)\n\n## KEY INSIGHT\nThe hybrid scoring does NOT filter constant-format tokens (they score high).\nThese need a SEPARATE filter: freq >= 150 as \"metaprogramming contamination\".\nFinal filter: (score > 0.4) AND (freq < 150)\n\n## Pending\n- [x] Design experiment (2026-03-24)\n- [ ] Implement scoring formulas\n- [ ] Run on pulse corpus\n- [ ] Compare precision/recall curves\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774379995144}}
